ally swept away by the Soviet-German War, the German invasion of Soviet Russia, and the Holocaust. The book makes a significant contribution to the history of the Holocaust and Second World War in the Soviet Union, presenting one Soviet region as an illustration of wartime social and media politics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aHolocaust, Jewish (1939-1945)zCaucasus, Northern. 0aJewsxPersecutionszSoviet UnionxHistoryy20th century. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945zCaucasus, Northern. 7aHISTORY / Holocaust.2bisacsh  aAshkenazi Jews.  aBolsheviks.  aCaucasus.  aEvacuation.  aFlight.  aGerman invasion.  aGinsburgs.  aHolocaust.  aJewish resistance.  aJewish.  aNazi Germany.  aPale of Settlement.  aRed Army.  aRefugee.  aRostov-on-Don.  aRussia.  aShoah.  aSoviet-German War.  aSoviet.  aUSSR.  aWWII.  aWorld War II.  aantisemitism.  aconcentration camps.  adiaspora.  aepistolary history.  afamily.  afascism.  agenocide.  aghettos.  aletters.  amacrohistory.  amedia.  amicrohistory.  amilitary.  apogrom.  apoverty.  apropaganda.  aracism.  awartime politics.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAcademic Studies Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068820708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP ROW Ebook Package English 20